## 📚 Key Takeaways

* Security Groups are AWS's built-in virtual firewall.
* They control inbound and outbound network traffic.
* Terraform allows Security Groups to be defined and managed as code.
* Following least privilege principles improves infrastructure security.
* Security Groups are a foundational component of AWS networking and cloud security.

